  ('social-worker-moex-00071', 'social-worker', 'social-worker-moex-114-7c9828ae', 'sub-social-worker-02', NULL, 'single_choice', '當地震災後，社會工作者向災民說明緊急安置的選項，包括組合屋、永久屋或搬去和親友居住， 以尊重服務對象意願。此符合社會工作倫理中那一個原則？', '["自由自主原則", "最小傷害原則", "保護生命原則", "差別平等原則"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T04:30:00+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "94a8952cb470", "answer_pdf_sha1": "e7b3bb4d7f68", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "114030", "c": "103", "s": "0301", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "社會工作", "year": "114", "exam_name": "114年第一次專技人員高等考試營養師、護理師、社會工作師考試", "original_question_number": 27, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "socialworker", "db_exam_id": "social-worker"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('social-worker-moex-00072', 'social-worker', 'social-worker-moex-114-7c9828ae', 'sub-social-worker-02', NULL, 'single_choice', 'Biestek提出個案工作與服務對象的關係建立之原則，下列何者錯誤？', '["個別化", "無目的性的情感表達", "有控制的情感涉入", "非評斷的態度"]'::jsonb, 1, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T04:30:00+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "94a8952cb470", "answer_pdf_sha1": "e7b3bb4d7f68", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "114030", "c": "103", "s": "0301", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "社會工作", "year": "114", "exam_name": "114年第一次專技人員高等考試營養師、護理師、社會工作師考試", "original_question_number": 28, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "socialworker", "db_exam_id": "social-worker"}'::jsonb, NULL),
