  ('social-worker-moex-00074', 'social-worker', 'social-worker-moex-114-7c9828ae', 'sub-social-worker-02', NULL, 'single_choice', '關於文化勝任能力（culturalcompetence）的描述，下列何者正確？', '["美國社會工作教育協會將世界衛生組織的主流文化觀點納入倫理規範", "文化勝任能力不涉及權力的本質，只討論文化差異", "臺灣社會工作師倫理守則第4點規定，社會工作師應尊重主流文化所造成的社會現象", "社會工作者在提供服務過程中包容多元文化，且運用各種溝通技巧達到雙向理解"]'::jsonb, 3, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T04:30:00+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "94a8952cb470", "answer_pdf_sha1": "e7b3bb4d7f68", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "114030", "c": "103", "s": "0301", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "社會工作", "year": "114", "exam_name": "114年第一次專技人員高等考試營養師、護理師、社會工作師考試", "original_question_number": 30, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "socialworker", "db_exam_id": "social-worker"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('social-worker-moex-00075', 'social-worker', 'social-worker-moex-114-7c9828ae', 'sub-social-worker-02', NULL, 'single_choice', '有關社會安全網計畫中所需要協助的「脆弱家庭」，下列何者錯誤？', '["家中主要生計者突發性遭受資遣或非自願性失業", "天然災害等突發性事件導致家庭支持功能受損", "家庭暴力造成家庭成員身心健康堪慮", "自殺行為導致家庭成員未獲適當照顧"]'::jsonb, 2, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T04:30:00+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "94a8952cb470", "answer_pdf_sha1": "e7b3bb4d7f68", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "114030", "c": "103", "s": "0301", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "社會工作", "year": "114", "exam_name": "114年第一次專技人員高等考試營養師、護理師、社會工作師考試", "original_question_number": 31, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "socialworker", "db_exam_id": "social-worker"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('social-worker-moex-00076', 'social-worker', 'social-worker-moex-114-7c9828ae', 'sub-social-worker-02', NULL, 'single_choice', '下列何種服務狀況反映刻板化的性別意識？①與家長討論發展遲緩幼兒個別化家庭服務計畫', '["男 性服務對象中風但仍有語言的溝通能力，照護管理專員在評估需求時，只向妻子詢問案主的身體 功能、生活自理狀況", "進行離婚訴訟的家長，爭取子女監護權，評估教養子女能力，詢問身為 職業婦女的媽媽如何安排稚齡兒童，對父親則詢問兒童的祖母能否協助", "中年兒子長期照顧年 邁母親，母親因跌倒骨折住院，社會工作者邀集全體家人共同討論出院準備計畫", ""]'::jsonb, 2, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T04:30:00+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "94a8952cb470", "answer_pdf_sha1": "e7b3bb4d7f68", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "114030", "c": "103", "s": "0301", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "社會工作", "year": "114", "exam_name": "114年第一次專技人員高等考試營養師、護理師、社會工作師考試", "original_question_number": 32, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": ["incomplete_options"], "slug": "socialworker", "db_exam_id": "social-worker"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('social-worker-moex-00077', 'social-worker', 'social-worker-moex-114-7c9828ae', 'sub-social-worker-02', NULL, 'single_choice', '非直系血親的雙方，經過法律認可的過程，建立親子關係，使失依兒童覓得永久家庭，同時也為 另一方覓得子女。係屬下列何種服務？', '["家庭寄養", "收養", "脆弱家庭服務", "安置服務"]'::jsonb, 1, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T04:30:00+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "94a8952cb470", "answer_pdf_sha1": "e7b3bb4d7f68", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "114030", "c": "103", "s": "0301", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "社會工作", "year": "114", "exam_name": "114年第一次專技人員高等考試營養師、護理師、社會工作師考試", "original_question_number": 33, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "socialworker", "db_exam_id": "social-worker"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('social-worker-moex-00078', 'social-worker', 'social-worker-moex-114-7c9828ae', 'sub-social-worker-02', NULL, 'single_choice', '有關建構社會工作（constructivesocialwork）之實務工作原則，下列何者正確？', '["目的在改變服務對象所處之社會結構", "建立服務對象的社會支持系統是首要方針", "應多發掘服務對象自身的敘說與詮釋", "服務對象的問題主要來自權力壓迫"]'::jsonb, 2, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T04:30:00+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "94a8952cb470", "answer_pdf_sha1": "e7b3bb4d7f68", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "114030", "c": "103", "s": "0301", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "社會工作", "year": "114", "exam_name": "114年第一次專技人員高等考試營養師、護理師、社會工作師考試", "original_question_number": 34, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "socialworker", "db_exam_id": "social-worker"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('social-worker-moex-00079', 'social-worker', 'social-worker-moex-114-7c9828ae', 'sub-social-worker-02', NULL, 'single_choice', '自助團體在1970年代開始就已經是精神康復服務重要的一環，其相關理念包含：同儕支持（Peer Support）、自助（Self-Help）、互助（MutualAid）、同儕心理治療（PeerPsychotherapy）等，關於 這些理念的敘述，下列何者正確？', '["「同儕支持」中提供對等的彼此支持、鼓勵和安慰的精神康復人士是屬於半專業人士", "精神病康復中的「自助」單純是指病人和康復者自行解決精神病所導致的困難", "「互助」著重發展一套完整理念、系統、思維和干預方法，建構網絡以取代／補償正式服務的 不足", "「同儕心理治療」是以過來人的經歷做為治療基礎"]'::jsonb, 3, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T04:30:00+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "94a8952cb470", "answer_pdf_sha1": "e7b3bb4d7f68", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "114030", "c": "103", "s": "0301", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "社會工作", "year": "114", "exam_name": "114年第一次專技人員高等考試營養師、護理師、社會工作師考試", "original_question_number": 35, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "socialworker", "db_exam_id": "social-worker"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('social-worker-moex-00080', 'social-worker', 'social-worker-moex-114-7c9828ae', 'sub-social-worker-02', NULL, 'single_choice', '有關職場暴力的敘述，下列何者錯誤？', '["運用壓力管理方案、內部團體溝通訓練等方案，可有效預防職場暴力", "不當資遣是引發職場暴力的常見因素之一", "不僅要關注員工個人心理困擾，也要關注職場內部與外部政策的公正性", "要聚焦在找出有潛在暴力傾向的員工，提供心理治療"]'::jsonb, 3, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T04:30:00+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "94a8952cb470", "answer_pdf_sha1": "e7b3bb4d7f68", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "114030", "c": "103", "s": "0301", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "社會工作", "year": "114", "exam_name": "114年第一次專技人員高等考試營養師、護理師、社會工作師考試", "original_question_number": 36, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "socialworker", "db_exam_id": "social-worker"}'::jsonb, NULL)
